This algorithm is used in systems which require high accuracy like aerospace industry. In this method, if dp/dv is positive, the same direction is followed to reach Perturbing voltage of the array increases or decreases output power and gets close to maximum power point by keeping the next perturbation constant or reversing it in which dp/dv is zero. If dp/dv is negative, reverse direction should be followed to reach the intent point. Equation (8) presents three operating points of this algorithm.8∂P∂V=0,V=Vmpp∂P∂V>0,V<Vmpp∂P∂V0,VVmpp\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
